<div id="fb_tab">
<div id="fb_tab_l">Left</div>
<div id="fb_tab_r">&nbsp;<img src="images/fblogo_mini.gif" /></div> 
</div> 
<div id="fb_pg_wrapper">
<div id="fb_pg_body">
	Retourne la sous-cha&icirc;ne la plus &agrave; gauche d'une cha&icirc;ne de caract&egrave;res<br \>
<br \>
<div class="fb_sect_title">Syntaxe</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><tt><br \>
<a href="KeyPgDeclare.html">Declare</a> <a href="KeyPgFunction.html">Function</a> <b>Left</b> <a href="KeyPgOverload.html">Overload</a> ( <a href="KeyPgByref.html">ByRef</a> <i>str</i> <a href="KeyPgAs.html">As</a> <a href="KeyPgConstQualifier.html">Const</a> <a href="KeyPgString.html">String</a>, <a href="KeyPgByval.html">ByVal</a> <i>n</i> <a href="KeyPgAs.html">As</a> <a href="KeyPgInteger.html">Integer</a> ) <a href="KeyPgAs.html">As</a> <a href="KeyPgString.html">String</a><br \>
<a href="KeyPgDeclare.html">Declare</a> <a href="KeyPgFunction.html">Function</a> <b>Left</b> ( <a href="KeyPgByref.html">ByRef</a> <i>str</i> <a href="KeyPgAs.html">As</a> <a href="KeyPgConstQualifier.html">Const</a> <a href="KeyPgWstring.html">WString</a>, <a href="KeyPgByval.html">ByVal</a> <i>n</i> <a href="KeyPgAs.html">As</a> <a href="KeyPgInteger.html">Integer</a> ) <a href="KeyPgAs.html">As</a> <a href="KeyPgWstring.html">WString</a><br \>
</tt><br \>
</div><div class="fb_sect_title">Usage</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><tt><br \>
<i>result</i> = <b>Left</b>[$]( <i>str</i>, <i>n</i> )<br \>
</tt><br \>
</div><div class="fb_sect_title">Param&egrave;tres</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
<tt><i>str</i></tt><br \>
<div class="fb_indent">La cha&icirc;ne de caract&egrave;res source.<br \>
</div><tt><i>n</i></tt><br \>
<div class="fb_indent">Le nombre de caract&egrave;res &agrave; retourner &agrave; partir de la cha&icirc;ne de caract&egrave;res source.<br \>
<br \>
</div></div><div class="fb_sect_title">Valeur retourn&eacute;e</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
Retourne la sous-cha&icirc;ne la plus &agrave; gauche &agrave; partir de <tt><i>str</i></tt>.<br \>
<br \>
</div><div class="fb_sect_title">Description</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
Retourne les <tt><i>n</i></tt> caract&egrave;res les plus &agrave; gauche &agrave; partir du d&eacute;but de <tt><i>str</i></tt>. Si <tt><i>str</i></tt> est vide, alors la cha&icirc;ne nulle (<tt>"</tt><tt>"</tt>) est retourn&eacute;e. Si <tt><i>n</i> &lt;= 0</tt> alors la cha&icirc;ne nulle (<tt>"</tt><tt>"</tt>) est retourn&eacute;e. Si <tt><i>n</i> &gt; len(<i>str</i>)</tt> alors la cha&icirc;ne enti&egrave;re est retourn&eacute;e.<br \>
<br \>
</div><div class="fb_sect_title">Exemple</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
<tt><div class="freebasic">
<span class="key">Dim</span>&nbsp;<span class="wrd">text</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">As</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">String</span>&nbsp;<span class="oth">=</span>&nbsp;<span class="quo">"hello&nbsp;world"</span><br />
<span class="key">Print</span>&nbsp;<span class="key">Left</span><span class="oth">(</span><span class="wrd">text</span><span class="oth">,</span>&nbsp;<span class="num">5</span><span class="oth">)</span><br />
</div></tt><br />
produira la sortie:<br \>
<br \>
<pre class="fb_pre">hello
</pre>Un exemple Unicode:<br \><br \>
<tt><div class="fb_box"><tr><td>dim text as wstring*20<br \>
text = "&#1055;&#1088;&#1080;&#1074;&#1077;&#1090;, &#1084;&#1080;&#1088;!"<br \>
print left(text, 6) 'displays "&#1055;&#1088;&#1080;&#1074;&#1077;&#1090;"<br \>
</div></tt></td><div style="clear:both">&nbsp;</div><br \>
</div><div class="fb_sect_title">Diff&eacute;rences de plate-forme</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
<ul><li> DOS ne supporte pas la version large <b><tt>WString</tt></b> de la cha&icirc;ne de <b><tt>Left</tt></b>.<br \>
<br \>
</ul></div><div class="fb_sect_title">Diff&eacute;rences de dialecte</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
<ul><li> Le suffixe de type de cha&icirc;ne "$" est obligatoire dans le dialecte <i><a href="CompilerOptlang.html">-lang qb</a></i>.<br \>
<li> Le suffixe de type de cha&icirc;ne "$" est facultatif dans les dialectes <i><a href="CompilerOptlang.html">-lang fblite</a></i> et <i><a href="CompilerOptlang.html">-lang fb</a></i>.<br \>
<br \>
</ul></div><div class="fb_sect_title">Diff&eacute;rences avec QB</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
<ul><li> QB ne supporte pas Unicode.<br \>
<br \>
</ul></div><div class="fb_sect_title">Voir aussi</div><div class="fb_sect_cont"><br \>
<ul><li> <tt><a href="KeyPgRight.html">Right</a></tt><br \>
<li> <tt><a href="KeyPgMidfunction.html">Mid (Function)</a></tt><br \>
<br \>
</ul></div>
</div>
